oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: WOPI event
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of Leo Carillo, left, at an event for WOPI in Bristol as part of the radio station's 25th anniversary celebration. Carillo is dressed as Pancho, his character in the show The Cisco Kid. The man standing beside him is holding WOPI microphone.
